\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And then got a - put his head on railway line - him that were coachman and he got coachman's - job then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And as coachman do you know just what he did? He actually drove the coach of the mill owner, was that it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And that was Robert Clough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. Sir John Clough. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And he owned Robert Cloughs at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What sort of a job was it, was it just a question of a five day week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - seven day a week job. Nights and all sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he was his only coachman and he took him wherever he went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well he had a groom with him like 
because they had - they had two pairs of - carriage horses and - one for single carriage, and then they had about - seven riding horses for young ladies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He had some daughters did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did he do this job until retiring, or did he do another job between then and retiring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well he were coachman 'til they selled the horses and then when they bought a - they bought an electric brougham first, one of them battery driven old - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}London{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose} electric brougham, he drove that. It just looked like a - a carriage without horses, he was sat up at front on it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It ran on batteries did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
They charged it up on - at mill on mill electric and - he run that for a while. And it were always running - batteries running down and leaving the old man stranded and - so -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did the old man drive it himself or did your father drive it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, me father drove it. And then - two sons - got fed up with hearing about it breaking down and one thing and another and so they got shot of it and bought a Daimler and then he drove that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So your father drove a Daimler?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He became a chauffeur?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How long did he do this job for, acting as chauffeur to Sir John Clough? Did he do that until retiring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did yes, 'til he finished. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And how old was he when he retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well he had - he gave up owing to sickness like and - he died when he were sixty-five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he retired before sixty-five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. About sixty-three or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he worked much of his working life as you did for Cloughs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh he worked all his life at Cloughs practically, bar - bit of time that he went to Merral}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12334879\charrsid10564979 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 s when he - was a boy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember your father ever being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. Oh no, never out of work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was your mother about the same age as your father do you remember? How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well she died in 1923. And she were about fifty-two when she - she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So your mother would be twenty-eight when you were born. Do you know where she came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She came - she were a - she were in service somewhere. I don't know whether it Steighton Hall or not.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Before being in service was she from this area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 From Rawden. Near {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Leeds{\*\xmlclose}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was that the only job she did before being married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When she was married did she carry on working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well she did - only - she did laundering for - fancy laundering for - house, for Cloughs. All this fancy goffering and - starching, maid's hats and all their - fancy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Anything that was a bit sort of fiddly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did she do that for a long time after being married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I think she did. Aye, she'd do it - she'd do it nearly to - end of first world war. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She managed to carry on doing it when she had the five little ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did they bring that work to her here at the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, they used to bring it, mm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So she didn't have to leave the children with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no. No. They brought it. One of men from mill brought it in a sk}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12334879\charrsid10564979 e}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 p and - took it at Friday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Is a skep one of those big baskets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Aye. Big baskets on - little wheels it were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So it was a sort of part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You told me that she died in 1923 so between once she finished doing this job for Cloughs did she not work any more?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She was always able to look after the children herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 YES. Oh aye. Look after - look after other folks and all many a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I should like to ask you about life
 at home when you were a child, the time up to when you left school. I think the house you lived in for the longest period was Wesley Place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 56 right across there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Could you tell there how many rooms were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh just a house and a kitchen. Mm. One large bedroom, one small bedroom and - attic.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you had a bedroom in the attic did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. With a dormer window like, it weren't a skylight window.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was a proper window?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did anyone else besides your parents and brothers and sisters live in the house? Did you have any relatives or lodgers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother ever pay anyone to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. She couldn't afford - on eighteen bob a week. She used to go out and help some other folk if she could and a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12334879\charrsid10564979 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 de a bob or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was the washing done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother or father mend or make the family clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, neither of 'em. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She never}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12334879\charrsid10564979  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
made the girls dresses or anything?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't re - no, I don't think she were a - sewer that way like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about mending?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh she - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would the clothes that you got be new or would they be second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12334879\charrsid10564979  }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 New.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She always bought you new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, certainly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there any handing down from child to child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh I daresay there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But when they were taken into the family they'd be new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You'd be the last in line for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you got new clothes do you remember which shop they bought them from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh now I can't tell you them days. A lot of 'em we - were - a chap used to come round, old - a chap called old Blair, the packman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And he sold dresses and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He used to sell - nearly anything, shoes or - anything, yes, he used to sell nearly anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He had some sort of cart did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Don't know how he used to get round, used to have a big case and come round and take orders one week and - it was so much a week you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And then he'd come round collecting the money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Yes, came every week like. Collecting his money and - if you give him a order he'd bring it following week. Aye, well there used to be a lot of that done in the old days. Oh aye.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And he'd just have this big case and show you what he had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about your shoes, did you get your shoes from him as well? Or would you go to a shop for those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I should imagine we should both get some at shop and some off him like, it just depend how things were
. If - if she'd any brass I expect she'd buy 'em locally and - if she hadn't well she'd get 'em off -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 If you bought shoes would you be taken down into Keighley to buy them or would there be a shop around here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, had to go into town. Oh - there
 used to be a Co-op up there but I don't think me mother was much of a Co-oper. I think we should go into town then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember the shop that sold the shoes where you used to go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh now then, now - don't know what that'd be - in them days, so long since.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But it was a private shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Do you remember when you would get new clothes and new shoes? Would they be bought just when they were absolutely worn out or would it be at a certain time of the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - it'd be any time really when they were - when we wanted 'em sort of thing like there was no special time about it like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When it was necessary to buy them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How about clogs, did you have to wear clogs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I wore - well, I don't know whether our girls did but we did. 'Cos I used to like clogs, I'd wear clogs now if I dare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Are they comfortable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - makes shoes into fits.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there a clogger around here where you bought the clogs from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, oh aye, used to go up to old - Billy Diddlers at - up there and he used to mend the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not that one just past the cross roads?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, just up by White Horse, up above - you know White Horse. Used to be Co}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12334879\charrsid10564979 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 perative clogg}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12334879\charrsid10564979 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
rs did that and then there were one on Ingrow Bridge you know. Old Jacobs, we used to go to either of them and - they used to measure you and make you a pair of clogs in - no time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You had shoes as well didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, always had shoes at Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you wore clogs on a Saturday and for school during the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, always wore 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, very little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did he ever help her with the cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, never seen him - never remembered him doing it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever see him doing some cooking for her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about fires in the morning, would he make a fire for her before going to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I don't think so. No. Well he - he were - he were out with them - with carriage 
while midnight and - had to be down at stable again by six or seven o'clock on a morning, well - he hadn't time for to help at home really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He worked fantastically long hours didn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh there was no hours in them days you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And there was no overtime involved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh, no overtime, overtime was a thing unheard of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And he earned about eighteen shillings a week for doing all these hours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Even at that time they were long hours for the pay weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh absolutely wicked. Well when I started}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12334879\charrsid10564979  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 work I used to work fifty-five and a half hours for seven shilling a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was the house at Wesley Place your own or rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, it were firms, rented.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So would he do any decorating to it in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did he ever do any repairs or improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember him ever helping with dressing the children, you and the others, did he ever help to dress you or to bath you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I can - I can never remember it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You'd be the youngest after the other one died wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember him ever reading to you or telling you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember him ever taking you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh aye, I used to go out w
ith him a lot. In - in - single dog - single dog cart like, carriage. Same as when he were going out - round farms collecting eggs for house and - I used to go out with him when he were taking horses out for exercise I used to go riding - with him when he
 were - when I were quite young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was it just you he took or did he take your brother or either of the two girls?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't think he did take our Tom a right lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I suppose you were the little one and he would take you more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he would never take you in the coach when he was taking the family out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It would be just when he was doing something by himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Only when he - when he were going out exercising or when he were going out, they used to go out
 at - in summertime and buy eggs you know, off farmers for them to pickle up at house you know. Used to get about - eighteen to dozen. Som}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 ma}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 t like that you know. Shillings a dozen and they'd get eighteen to dozen and - all that sort - he used to go where he could get best - where he could make a bob or two for hissen I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He wouldn't tell them he was getting them as cheap as that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no, no, make a bob or two for hissen I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he did quite a few jobs for Cloughs other than just actually driving the coach?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well, he did a lot for hisself, he used to cut - cut hor - horses round here at - Saturday and Sunday - when they weren't busy, when he weren't out with - clip 'em you now. Trim 'em. Other people's horses. Railway, he used 
to do all railway horses, both Midland and GM. And then there were lots of - a lot - lots of people had horses then in them days for their work you know and - he used to do them. I used to be - twining machine down there and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He would go to their stables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, they used to bring 'em here. 'Cos it were a big machine on a stand you know with - a big wheel, I should think - that big were wheel you know and he had to twine it and then there were a band and a - little wheel and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What was this for doing? What did it cut, this machine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Used to trim horses, cut 'em - cut 'em their hair, you know how they cut 'em and - cut 'em all -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Cut all their hair?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not all that, they - leave a straight line across the body, you've seen horses - 
on television when they're cut. Some of race horses is cut the same way today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They did it with a machine did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So did he have a stable of his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, he did it down here when they were - on quiet. Well they'd know 
he were doing it I expect be somebody tell 'em because there were - always somebody that'd tell.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And down here was Cloughs stables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Cloughs stables you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It wasn't up at the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh no. No. No, the stables were down here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And he would sort of get the horse and coach ready and take it up to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Mm. Well he used to bring - Sir John down to mill every morning. And then Mrs Clough were an invalid and he used to take her out in the invalid carriage. He used to take he
r out in that of afternoon when it were nice. Then if Sir John were going to Bradford he'd have to run him to the station. Meet him when he came back from Bradford, and - all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he'd travel about on the railways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Then - girls
'd want - three saddled horses at eleven o'clock or sommat like that and he'd have to dash back and get three saddled horses ready, take them up for them and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You said Mrs Clough had an invalid carriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was it a special sort of carriage that she could lie down in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Yes. Rec - sort of - long reclining - carriage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She could lie down in it could she?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were never actually taken hout, you and the other children, for a morning or an afternoon without your mother being there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was just you that he would take out with him when he was doing his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember him ever looking after you when she was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. Never remember her going out so much. She never had time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have any tasks that you had to carry out regularly at home to help your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well I had no tasks but I used to help though, I used to help - when she were ironing if she were tired I'd do a bit of plain ironing or - I used to use the old Singer sewing machine and do a bit of sewing for her. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What would you sew, would it be a bit of repairing or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye. Any sort of straight sewing I used to do. Plain ironing like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How long did you continue to do little jobs like this, after you left school or did you stop once you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well I don't think I - well, I would do occasionally after I started work occasionally but - I don't think it'd be as often when I were - after I started work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about your brothers and sisters, did they have any jobs that they had to do about the house to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well we used to have a paper round, he used to take papers - but - evening papers like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He'd make a few shillings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would that have to be given to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, he used to give it - to me mother.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So it was his way of helping out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he didn't do any actual household tasks? This was his job was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, he used to have this evening paper round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about the sisters, what did they do about the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well, they'd help me mother, well what oldest sister especially, young 'um were right keen - me youngest sister weren't right keen on housework but me old
est sister used to - they used to call out a lot and - she used to give her a hiding now and again did the oldest sister like. Because she were dodging work like, she weren't - one that wanted to be off and out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What sort of jobs would your elder sister help with, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh, anything in the house. Any housework, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She didn't have any particular jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no. No. No, she'd - she were always one that were helping me mother were eldest - girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember the elder 
children helping the younger ones with things that they found difficult, such as dressing or eating? Before your younger brother died could you remember your eldest sister helping to look after the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, they would do I daresay but I can't - no recollection of it really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You don't remember them helping you with anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, well I was one that could help meself as far as I can -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember there being anything that you helped them with? Anything that you ever did for the 
older children when you were a little boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well I used to - I used to take our Tom in kitchen and wash his neck and his ears, he were a beggar for dodging his - and he was older than me. I used to take him in kitchen, mother used to - 'cos he were a 
bit stupid, and - me mother used to give me a nudge and - tell me and I used to - get him in kitchen and - work - wash his neck for him and wash his ears out for him and - 'cos he were a bit of dodger for washing like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would he he what you would term now mentally subnormal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well, he weren't - he were just - he weren't - we-l you could call - he weren't mental, but he were just a little bit - sort of stupid sort of thing you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 A bit slower than you w-re?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He had to be helped?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, oh yes, to ordinary school and all that sort of thing, aye, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were children were you all expected to go to bed at a certain time when you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I don't know as we'd a certain time but we had to be in in reasonable time like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So they didn't have a fixed time for you to be all in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, we didn't say at eight o'clock or seven o'clock or owt like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When your mother decided you'd to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother or anyone else put you to bed when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, would when we were very small but like after we were able to get undress ourself and that like we used to get ourselves off to bed.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you know how old you'd be when you started to put yourself to bed? Would you be quite young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I - well I should, I don't know about any of the others but I should I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How old would you be about, can you remember? Would it be after you started school or before that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I think it'd be - before I started school. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you share the bedroom or bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 With me brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 At the house at Wesley Place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where did you and your brother sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Me and me brother slept in attic. Two girls slept in - big bedroom - in little bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you and your brother have a double bed that you shared?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And did the girls have a double bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And your parents slept in the large bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 At Wesley Place what room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
We used to have one of them tin baths and - bring it up out of cellar and bath in kitchen. We had one of them old coppers in corner of kitchen you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you'd heat the water in the copper in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And then ladle it out into bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How often would you have a bath at that time? Would it be a certain night of every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, when we needed one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So it would be up to your mother, when she decided you needed a bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Aye. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember how often you had clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How we had what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Clean clothes to put on. A change of clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - we never - we never - were short of clean clothes and - always were kept clean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you have a certain day of the week when you'd all put clean on, do you remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh I can't remember that. But I know - I know we - I know we always were kept clean and - clean clothes and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were all at home at Wesley Place where would you all have your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 In - the house. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were there any occasions when you would eat in another room, perhaps in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, always had the meals in the house like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where did your mother do all the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 In - kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did she have a range or was it a gas stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, she had a - not a gas oven, 'cos she never liked gas, she did all her cooking in - oven in - house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So she actually prepared things in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Kitchen. Brought it in - in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was a sort of oven range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Yes, with fire you know. She never liked gas. We had a little - one of them little rings with two burners on you know, in kitchen but - just for boiling water and boiling vegetables or owt of that but - all cooking she did in - in the oven in -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What time would you have breakfast? When you were all going to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh, any time between eight and half past.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Justin time to get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you be all present for breakfast, would your father be there as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh no, he wouldn't be there, he'd be off - before up - we got up probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How would he manage for his breakfast, would he make it himself or did he get something at Cloughs house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, he'd probably come up - home sometime and - have some breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Later in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm, happen after we'd gone to school. Many a time before we'd gone to school, it just depended on what - pop in when he had chance and -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So when you had breakfast in the morning there would be just all four of you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember what you usually had to eat and drink at breakfast time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, I don't remember exactly but we didn't have - we didn't have a lot of cooked breakfasts I know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you have anything different on Sunday perhaps for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 May have had - may have had a bit of sommat - special on a Sunday like for breakfast, I don't know. I can't really remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about the midday meal? What did you call the midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How do you go on about your dinner? What time would you have it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Between twelve and one.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were all at school did you all come home for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. Aye. I but went to that school just up there, it were only about - fifty yards you know, Wesley Place just up there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you would all come home for your dinner, was your father ever there for dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Most days he}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 d be - he'd be home for dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So all the family would be there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember what sort of a meal you would have for dinner, what your mother would give you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh I don't know, used to - we used to always have a good dinner I can tell you that. I couldn't tell you though - yes. We always h
ad a good cooked dinner, always, every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there usually meat with hit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 On a Sunday would you have anything different, anything special, was there any special meal that you had Sunday dinner time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, nowt special, only - we generally had a - bit of a joint at weekend like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And you wouldn't during the week, this would be something reserved specially for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, ayes, same as them days well they always did like make a special - day of Sunday dinner like, I 
don't know as there's any in Sunday and any other dinner really. They used to do in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You would have a joint, and would you have Yorkshire pudding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, always a - joint and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you used to finish with a sweet or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Aye, always had a - pudding or - something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would it be a rice pudding?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, various 'cos she were a good cook was mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you had a fairly varied diet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, we'd a - for working class people we had a good - good living
. 'Cos although me fath - dad had only eighteen - shilling a week, he never kept a ha'penny out of his wage - for hisself. He made all his spending money - with cutting horses and - all that sort of thing. Doctoring horses for people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He'd act as a part time vet as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 This money that your father earned, did he always keep it to himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - he would - treat me mother occasionally but most of it he spent on hisself, and - he liked his beer like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What time would you have tea? Was it straight after school or a bit later?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well - we used to - run in after school and we'd - always get a slice of bread and some butter and - jam or sommat of that sort but we'd have tea about - half past five or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would your father be in with you at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 If they weren't on - duty would be but he was sometimes he'd be out and sometimes he'd be in like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What sort of a tea would your mother make you during the week? Would it be a cooked tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 We
ll, wouldn't be cooked every day but - cooked occasionally like, same as she used to make - used to get some - fish and - mashed potatoes and rice and make 'em into fish cakes and - that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She'd make a little bit go a long way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever have potted meat or tripe or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well - we used to have tripe and we used to have potted meat but we - we used to make it ourself because - when me dad went shopping for Cloughs - at Saturday - they used to - get a b
it - shin and veal and all sorts off butchers at cheap and - we always had a - one of them old brown stew pots and - they used to bring - get that full - full and put it on and - leave it in the oven at Saturday night and - we used to have that sometimes 
f
or breakfast warm at Sunday morning and then it used to set and - me mother used to - pick all the bones out and make it into brawn you know. Aye. A brown stewpot about so big, and that - full every Saturday night when he were - when I were younger like, 
I don't know how old I - well - kids like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
When you say that your father used to get a bit of meat on the cheap, when he went to the butchers would they perhaps let him have meat cheaper in consideration of him bringing Cloughs order?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Cloughs trade. Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he would get perhaps
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He got a lot of benefits that way, with - with their trade you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Considering you had such a low wage you didn't seem to do badly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh we did - we did a lot better - folk that worked in mill actually as regards - food and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did this apply to - did he do most of the shopping for Cloughs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 YES? AYE, he used to go - either - well, young ladies when they grew up like used to go and - of course when they were in shop one of the
 assistants used to nip out and - shove him - something under the seat you know when he was sat up on seat and all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 This was all inconsideration of him bringing them to them sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 On a Sunday afternoon for tea would you have anything special?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well not usually, if there were owt special on, same as -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 The potted meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You don't remember having any fruit or anything as a special treat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not anything special.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You said your father never did any cooking of any kind, would your mother make her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Always. Well, she used to bake three times a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So she never bought bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, never - never dreamt of that, well - they wouldn't
 sell - they didn't sell bread like they do today in them days, there was only like one confectioners in the place. Same as ordinary shops didn't sell bread in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember her ever making her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 YES? SHE used to make her own jam and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember her bottling fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Crabapple jelly and - stuff like that, used to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember her bottling fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember her making pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Making pickles? No, she weren't a - well we were never a big - eater of pickles Sort of thing like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember her ever making wine or any medicines for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember her ever brewing beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your father or mother grow their own vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, me dad - we had an allotment during first world war. That's all. When that were - when that were dig for victory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What did your father grow there in the allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - potatoes, carrots, turnips, cabbage, anything in vegetable line.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It's amazing he found time to do all that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Mm. Well we did a lot of it like 'cos we were just like getting to be - fourteen or fifteen year old like and me and Tom used to go on and - mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother buy fruit and vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 YES. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember her ever buying any tinned or dried fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She used to buy - dried figs and dried prunes, thems all that I can remember her buying at dried fruit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You don't remember her buying tinned fruit or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, never. Not in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your father ever keep any livestock for the family such as hens or pigs or goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Used to keep rabbits. Feed 'em on - and - for eating you know, tame rabbits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They'd be fed on the horses diet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. Yes. Oats and bran and - stuff like they fed the horses on you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where did you keep the rabbits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He used to keep 'em in a - loose box down at stables. Grow mushrooms and all. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And he did this from you being quite small did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And you used to have the rabbits to eat occasionally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm. Well you couldn't get meat during first}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 world war like so - that's why we started keeping rabbits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You didn't have the rabbits until the war started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Who looked after the rabbits, was it just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, we'd go down and clean 'em out and look after 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember how many times a week you would have meat? Would it be every day or every other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
I couldn't say - I couldn't say exactly but - I should think we were having meat nearly every day for lunch. Or else fish or - something like that you know, we'd have good some - we'd a good lunch every day, always had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about tinned meat, do you ever remember your mother buying a tin of meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Do you ever remember getting extra meat such as a rabbit from poaching? Did you ever know anyone who did any poaching who would let you have a rabbit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well we had a - we knew a chap that used to always be rabbiting and he used to bring us one many a time. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He would be poaching would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 YES. Aye. On - on the moors. All over he used to go. He used to bring us a couple of rabbits many a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would he give them to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. He were a friend of the family like
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How often would he do this, would it be fairly frequently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, just depends how they were able to get out you know, and when he could go and that sort of thing. He always kept f
errets and dogs and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 This was how he caught them was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you ever remember seeing your mother having less food so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I can't really remember it but - she would have done if we'd have - if it had have been necessary, I know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your father have more than anyone else?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were all sat at the table, did you all used to sit at a table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well we'd have been allowed to do but I don't think we did a lot of talking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were too busy eating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But there was no restriction?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh there were no - restrictions on not talking that I can ever remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, we could - choose what were - what sort of were on like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What would your parents attitude be if you left some food uneaten on your plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well they wouldn't force you to eat it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They wouldn't mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
If there was something on the table you wanted like the salt, could you ask someone to pass it to you or did you have to wait until it was offered?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, if we wanted we should just ask if we couldn't reach it we'd ask somebody else to - pass it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, if there were any, if there was any second helping, any left like we could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She didn't mind you asking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way and sit in a certain way when you were at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you allowed to bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not at meal times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Any time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 As soon as you'd finished your meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 As soon as you finished your meal. Oh you didn't have to sit and wait to - somebody else finishing like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have to ask your parents permission to leave the table or could you just get down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I don't say that - I can remember asking really, but used to say, well - I've finished mam and - get - just get down sort of thing.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did all the family sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you always have the same places? Did you always sit in the same order round the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I think we would do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
How would the meal be served? Would it be served on the table itself in tureens or would your mother put all the food out on plates and give you your plates round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well she'd have it on table and she'd - dish it out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So she would use big dishes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And put it on each of your plates?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That's right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Your mother always did this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You oldest sister never did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What order would you be served in, would there be a special order?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, just - served out and that were it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where did - can you remember the brother who died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I can - only just faintly remember him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember where he'd sit for a meal, would it be up to the table or would he have a high chair or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I can't remember, I can only just vaguely remember Alec baby.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you don't remember who fed him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you say that your mother was an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Easy person to talk to, yes. Very.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was she the sort of person who would show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, very affectionate and understanding in every way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And she would show her affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 If you had any worries could you share them with her or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And what about your father, were you able to talk to him in the same way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, never had time much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Perhaps when you went on a ride on the cart with him, were you able to talk to him?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, oh yes, yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was he affectionate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, I wouldn't say he was affectionate really. I never remember him giving me a hapenny in me life 'til day I went Selsey and he gave me half a crown. The day I went sales with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he would never demonstrate his affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. He never gave us spending money. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He was never one for giving hugs or kisses or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would your mother do this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 If you had any worries could you share them with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, I daresay I could have done. I used to always go to me mother like, I were a - I were a mother's lad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would this be because she was always there do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I should think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well - me mother were a - I - I could describe her to you but she would - same as if she shouted after you, you'd never say - what? You'd say, yes mum or - something like that you know, if you'd have said what - sh
e'd have - given you a dressing down for saying what like, that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You'd to attend to what she said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about your father, was he similar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't think he were like I don't think. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He wasn't as involved perhaps?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. He weren't in - no, he weren't involved - very little with - bringing the children up like, me - mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, as long as you just - were all right and talked all right and treat 'em all right - everything went on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did they say you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. Never remember her - saying that to me like. We used to have childish squabbles same as any other children you know like but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
But you don't remember any of you coming home and saying that someone had hit you and her saying perhaps well you should have hit them back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't - no, I don't ever remember that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well mother used to always - used to always say - if you can't do any - anybody any good don't do 'em any harm, that's what she used to always drum into us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Is there anything else that you can think of, anything that your father used to say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't say now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you say that your parents brought you up to consider certain things as important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, trying to do right, that's the only thing that I can - s
ay like, you know. Me mother especially, she always - brought it in - drummed it into us about trying to do right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would she mean by this being honest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, being - trying to behave right and honest in all ways sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were all children and grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in the conversation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 If you did something that your parents disapproved of what would happen?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, I don't know, I can never remember me mother hitting me, and me father either, hitting me in me life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember them not hitting any of the other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well I can remember - I can remember 'em - hitting girls when they were falling out like, I remember me mother hitting girls when they were falling out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That's unusual isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about your brother, did he ever get smacked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, I can never remember her - her - anyway we'd never try anything like like. And we were - well, what would I be in that time, I'm seventy-one and he would be - seventy - four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So the thing that seemed to annoy her most was the fact that the girls squabbled was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She didn't smack anyone for anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well it used to be - it used to be - through me elder sister,
 she - she'd - be - falling out with Ethel 'cos Ethel wouldn't do this and woul}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 dn't do that and - they'd get ju}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
ggling and falling out and then me mother'd - give 'em both a hiding then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember when you were small doing anything wrong and bein
g punished in any other way, other than being smacked, perhaps having to do without spending money or perhaps being sent to bed early?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no. No, no, no. I don't remember - anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You don't remember your father doing anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, never remember me father hitting any one of us. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 So you can't remember a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
ny occasions at all when you were punished in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you say that you received the ideas you had about how to behave from both your paren
ts, or did one play a more important part than the other?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well me mother played a more important part rather than me dad like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was this just because she was always there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not much. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you receive any presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well - very rare. Only time we used to get - presents that I can remember was - at Christmas like, we always got - plenty of presents from the house and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They sent presents down did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, they always sent us books and presents at Christmas for all kiddies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When it was your birthday would you have anything special to eat at tea time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not as I know of. We didn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You wouldn't have friends in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Never had parties and that sort of thing that I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You don't remember asking just a particular friend in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember anything that you did with your mother and father together on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't remember owt - special like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You remember perhaps singing carols or playing any games, anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would your father be at home for Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He - he would have to go down to the stable and all that sort of thing and - 
if they were going any out at Christmas to any parties he'd have to be on - duty you see just the same.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't remember, never were a musical family. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You never had a piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Could any of you play an instrument?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I used to play drums, when I were younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you come to play the drums?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 With Scouts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have your own drums that you'd bring home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, I used to bring it home but it weren't mine like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did either of the sisters play an instrument?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did they ever sing, were your sisters singers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you never made music together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember your parents playing games with you when you were children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Never had time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You never remember them playing either cards or dominoes, anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't - I can't remember, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember there being any books in the house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, there's - books like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You say Cloughs used to send them down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, and then we used to get 'em from - school library and all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You had a school library did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, used to have a small school library up here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your parents have any books, were there any books for grown ups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would they take a newspaper, a daily newspaper perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I don't know about a daily, they took weekly local paper at week, that's the only one that I remem
ber, I don't think they - they'd buy one occasionally but I don't think they took it regular. Of course we used to have - apart when me brother - when me brother was taking papers like he'd have some left well we'd always get one that we could read like t
hat way sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They'd just get the weekly Keighley News?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They wouldn't get a Sunday paper at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, can't remember one. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about magazines, do you remember them getting a magazine of any kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I never - took magazine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember your mother or father sitting reading, in the evening perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Me mother more than me father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did they ever read aloud to you or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Your mother never read to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Do you remember ever going to a funeral in the family? Do you remember there ever being a funeral in the family, of a grandparent or an uncle or aunt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I went when I were - well when I went in the the Army when me grandfather died. That were first funeral I'd ever been to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It would be before 1919 wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 About 19 - 1917.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 We were talking about the funeral you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Your grandfather's in 1917.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were able to go to it although you were in the Army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I got leave, I were at Halifax then, I got leave and came - to go through to Rawdon like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was at Rawdon was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember who attended it, was it just the immediate family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Just the immediate family, then there'd be perhaps friends of his at Rawdon I expect like but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How many would there be there altogether do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - no idea. Be a good few because he were - he were an old Quaker and lived at - Meeting House
 Cottage at Rawdon like and looked after - after he retired he looked after - Quaker church there at - at Rawdon, Friend's Meeting House at Rawdon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So it would be a Quaker funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm. Well anybody speaks you know, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You stand up as the spirit moves you sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Yes. Aye. Yes. Same with a wedding. There's no minister you know. The friend any friend can read service and - any friend can sign marriage certificate, as many a time ten - signs marriage certificate.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 At this funeral did everyone wear mourning clothes, did you wear black?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No. No, I went in me khaki.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about the other people who weren't in the Army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well there'd be a lot of them in black 'cos they all - they used to all wear black in them days like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So most of the people were in mourning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Most people would be in - mourning like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They had the service at the friend's meeting house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Afterwards would they go back to his house for a tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, they had a tea at school across. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You all went there for a tea after the funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Weren't elaborate tea or owt of that like but cup of tea and just a bit of sommat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember when you were small ever being taken out visiting neighbours, or friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Oh well we used to go to Rawdon and - both me dad and mum used to take us to Rawdon. Mm. And - we used to go visit - me father's relations at Haworth, and that - all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So your mother and father would take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you ever taken shopping with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't recollect going shopping with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Your father got most of the shopping in did he?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When he did the shopping for Cloughs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Me mother did - same as all groceries and all such stuff as that, but he used to bring meat and - fish and - poultry now and again and -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You never went with him when he went for these things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no, he'd get 'em when he were out shopping for the family. He used -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You never went with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, I can't say - well I used to go up to - she used to send the order up to Co-op and I'd go up and - bring it. Used to bring - flour in a - pillowcase with a blue handkerchief tied round on top of your head and - b
ag in each hand. There were no - packaging like there is today you know, you had to take your own jar and wait - jar and - weigh treacle and all that sort of thing, and flour and sugar and everything were - were weighed out in them days, there were no pac
kaging like there is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever go out with just your father? You told me that he used to take you out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I used to go out with him - same as exercising the horses or - egg collecting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did he ever take you anywhere else other than with the horses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You said you went to his family at Haworth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, he'd - sometimes go on his own up to - woods or - up his Uncle John's at - Oakworth or anything like that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would he take the children with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 YES, on he'd take one or two of us with him then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember any other outings with your parents, perhaps at Bank Holidays? Do you remember ever all going out together as a family?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't. No, we never - well they never had no holidays didn't me father as I know on, I never heard tell of him having a holiday.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you said he used to go up to the woods, is that where someone lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well it were some relations of his that kept Vronte caf\'e9 at top of main street, Howarth. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They were called the Woods?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So he'd occasionally go there, you'd walk to Haworth presumably would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, you had to do in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Or go by train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Or go by - with valley train but we used to - you'd most - usually walk
 it. Or if he were - if - if they were away or if they weren't wanting it he'd the old - dog cart and - single horse up and take us up on that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He was allowed to do this was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, aye, when - well I don't know whether he were allowed but - he used to do it when he knew - things were all right like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember ever going away for a holiday, all of you together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, never - I used to go - stop at Rawdon with me grandma. When I were a kiddy like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you go by yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, me mother and father perhaps take me and then come - for me in a week or two or something like that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Those were the only holidays you ever had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Them were only holidays before were, them were holi - only holidays I know never went to Blackpool or - anything like that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You never went to Blackpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you never even go for a day to Blackpool, or Morecambe?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not before - not before 1918 - war - 14/18 war like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So when you went off in the Army in the 14/18 war it was the first time you'd been away from home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did none of the other children ever go on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They never went to Rawdon to stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well of course they only had - they only used to have f
our days at - what they called - usual holiday, Parish Feast Holiday, used to only have four days then. Used to only have a day at Easter and Whitsun and - such as that like, hadn't time to go on holidays then. Well you hadn't brass to go on holidays neve
r mind owt else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you actually never saw the sea until you were older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, not 'til - 'til after the first world war. Well I saw it when I were in war like, when I went across to France. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you went to grandmas house what would you do while you were there to amuse yourself? Were there friends you could play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh there were - kiddies there than I knew like my age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there anything particularly you used to do with your grandparents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I used to go with him 
- he kept - some hens, he were retired from a quarry down Harpley Lane and - I used to go down with my grandfather to feed hens on a morning and night. Then I used to go walking to Haden with him, shopping. All that sort of thing like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Could you tell 
me how you spent your Saturdays in those days, when you were still at school? What would you do on a Saturday, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Now, oh, watch cricket sometimes on - Ingrow on Damens Road. Well that's about as far as we used to get.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How about on a Sunday, what would you do on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, Sun - Sunday school and - used to go both morning and afternoon.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What Sunday school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 St Johns. Church - Ingrow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Your father was Church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I don't think he were - I don't think he - me mother - me mother were brought up a Quaker, but - you see \{BLANK\}
 to go to the Quakers, well - she went to Church of England when she went - when she were in Ingrow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you say this was more for convenience?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 More for convenience than -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have any different clothes to put on on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, we always had some - best clothes for Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you play any games on a Sunday? Or did your parents think it wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well if we did play games it'd be - out of their sight sort of thing, we may have done but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They didn't like you to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were they very strict about this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not particularly strict like but - you knew the
y didn't like it - you playing games like. I mean to say same as all lads we used to do many a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother go to St Johns?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Oh yes, she went - fairly regularly there. To church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your father ever go with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not unless it wer}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 e a - wedding or a funeral or so}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 mmat of that like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You went to Sunday school in the morning and afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you go to church services as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I - I did 'til I were about fourteen and then - or would I be so old
. No, I was - I were half time - at time and - and I - it would - anniversary Sunday and - I know me mother couldn't afford me a new suit, and - I had an aunt lived near and she run me}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979  }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
pair of trousers up at - at Saturday and - me mother bought me a jers
ey and I went to - anniversary in this and - they were new - both new like but - old parson pulled me out in front of class and said it weren't a football match and I never went now more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That was when you were twelve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Aye, when I were about twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And everyone else had new suits on presumably?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - they'd all - it used to be a regular thing like you know. And it - it -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you used to get new suits usually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Usually, but it were just a matter of - this case it were a case
 that - they just couldn't afford one or something of that sort at time and - I know I - I never went no more, I never went neither to Sunday school nor church after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And you'd been a regular attender until then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Been a regular attender 'til then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was the vicar who did that was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, old Askew.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What did your mother say when you told her about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh she were very upset. 'Cos I mean to say we'd - we'd little to spare in them days and they were building church 
institute, and there were a fund for it and she were giving sixpence a week to fund for - church institute, help to build that. And she stopped that and all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was anything said to the vicar?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, we daren't have said owt to him - they couldnt' get me to go no more after that, I wouldn't go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did he actually send you out of the building?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, he just pulled me out in front of all other children and said s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 o}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 mmat about this - weren't a football match or s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
mmat of that like, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But he allowed you to remain for the rest of the period?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was something that just - well I couldn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did the other children say anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They didn't pull your leg?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no. Well never went no more. I wouldn't go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You'd be embarrassed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you still went to Sunday school before you were twelve do you remember there being any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, we used to have one every - were it Whitsun - yes, Whitsun - Whit Monday. We used to 
meet at - all meet at church - school yard you know and - and we used to march and sing and - and go into one of Haggas' fields up at the top of Ingrow Lane there and then there were - currant buns and tea and - games and - all that sort of thing. Whit Mo
nday walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you walk in procession?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would there be a brass band?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, usually a band and - teachers every so often you know with so many children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And they would take you to this field?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 A sort of gala?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That was the one outing per year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They never had a sort of wagonette sort of outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, I can't remember none.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember any other social activities being organized by the church? That you took part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did they ever have any concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were a member of the scouts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. Mm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you remain a member of the scouts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I gave up with scouts, I gave up - because it were church scouts I were in you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember the church having any - you were never in the choir were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, were never a singing family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember if the church ran a temperance club?
