\insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 mmat of that sort.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you a member of the Band of Hope?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What activities did it have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well just have a - bit of a meeting at Monday night and I expect they used to lecture us on - evils and one 
