\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were at home was grace said at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can never remember it. At home I can't anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you taught to say prayers at night before going to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Politics? Well - I don't - I don't 
- I couldn't say whether he did or not but - like when the elections were on he used to be out with - carriage all day with bows of yellow ribbon on the horses like, Sir John were a Liberal - they used to bring voters in for - Liberals like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You wouldn't know what his views were then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't know his views on politics.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember him ever voting in a general election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, they'd always vote then. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I think women got the vote in 1918, do you remember your mother voting in a general election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
I can't say you see for - I - I'd - I were away from 1917 'til about - 1919. And then she died in 23, well - I should imagine she would use it. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When your father did vote do you know which party he would vote for? Did he ever tell you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No. Well he'd be supposed to vote for Liberals like whether - they did or not I don't know like but - I mean to say everybody that worked for Cloughs there in them days had to vote Liberal. Well they said they did anyway, whethe
r they did or not If you worked for Haggas's you were Tories but if you worked at Cloughs you were Liberals.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
What about going to church, was there anything to do with religion in this, whether you worked at Cloughs or Haggas's? Did Cloughs go to the chapel or the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They went - Methodist down here. Well they kept it going for years you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And Haggas's were church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, you hadn't to go with them. They never interfered with your religion at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You said the people who worked at Cloughs were expected to vote Liberal by their employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, you had to say you were Liberal whether you were or not like in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 In some places at that time men flet that they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh well they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure, to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, oh yes, definitely, they were all were in these houses them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think that they all actually voted Liberal or do you think they were all afraid of saying that they voted anything different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well they'd be afraid of saying ay - any different, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So they definitely felt themselves under this sort of pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 OH yes, them - in them days they definitely did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I wonder if they would dare to vote for another party although they would never mention it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, there's lots on 'em'd - would vote for - Lib - for Conservatives or Labour party. Old - be old
 Labour party, Old ILP in them days you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But not mention it to anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh no, they daren't mention it, so - firm got to know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember anyone actually losing their job because of being involved with perhaps the ILP?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, can't say as I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You said your father wasn't political, was he a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You don't remember him working - actually he would work for one of the parties wouldn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well he did like when - at the election days like. That's right, for - Cloughs like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He would used the coach to go around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, used to run - old people up to the school to vote you know from -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was it ever used to take people from the mill to vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No. If ever anybody
 was taken ill at work - he used to have to run them home like and that sort of thing, I can remember him being called out for that many a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But not for voting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your parents take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
When your parents were not doing their work, I know they were both kept very busy, but when they did have any spare time how would they spend it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well me father'd spend all his spare time at - what spare time he had he'd spend at club or pub I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He was a member of a club was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Conservative Club. He were a member of both Conservative and Liberal club. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother have any interests outside her home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well she never had time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself, did she ever have time to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, can never remember her going out at lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - oh well he used to come home - teat
ime and then many a time he'd be out while two o'clock if they were at - parties and that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So how many evenings would be spent at home in the course of a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Me father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You said he was a member of two clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Aye, be luck - he'd be lucky if he got one week at home - one night at home, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So it was quite rare that he spent a full evening at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Very rare he were in at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother not mind, the fact that he was at work so often and when he did have a free night he'd go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, she didn't mind at all. Of course he used to be clipping horses and - going out doctoring horses and - and then there were dog breeder used to breed dogs and - sell dogs and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 At the stables? He had dogs at the stables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye. Plenty of loose boxes and we always - bred fox terriers and Irish terriers down at stable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They were his own dogs were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye. Well they used to supply all - better end round here with dogs, in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They were pedigree?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, they were pedigree - dogs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your father attend any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Attend any what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Clubs or pubs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He was a member of the Conservative Club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He were a Conservative Club and he were a member at Liberal Club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there a pub that was his local that he used to go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh aye, go down to - valley at White Horse I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He went fairly regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother ever go with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your father ever take part in any sport that you can remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't remember him - ever taking part in any sport. But he were a wonderful fit man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did he ever attend the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Attend the races? No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did he ever have a bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not as I can tell. Of course I didn't know nowt about - racing in the days like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your father or mother belong to any sort of savings club, either a boot club or a sick club or a funeral club, anything like that?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 There was no one ever coming to collect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Oh no, no. Oh used to be that little - there used to be a ha'penny Brief - in them days. You paid ha'penny a week and you got so much for a death and - that sort of thing. It - it were called Little Brief, it were - 
funeral do of some sort. Little Brief, I don't know - went out of existence, of course it were only a ha'penny a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And that helped pay for a funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, if anybody had a death like they got so much out of this Little Brief.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 A sort of funeral club then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 This man who used to come and sell clothes and shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That would be a sort of club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, well it was sort of a club, you paid so much a week and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember them being in any sort of sick club if they were off ill you got so much a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No. No, I joined }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid879019\charrsid10564979  Odd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 -fellow}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 s when I came out of - first world war like and I've been a member ever since at Odd
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 -fellow}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 s like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But your father was never a member?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 All right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there one that you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, me eldest sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Why do you think this was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I don't know, we just seemed to have a - more affection for one
 another. Of course I - I really had for all the lot but - more so her than - any of the others.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Has this continued through out your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Aye, up 'til her died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were a child who did you play with, your brother and sisters or the neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, I used to have - different friends like. That - the same as that one that she's just come in about now and - another old chap that I play with. Snooker of afternoon down at Reading Room, like the - one or two that I went - we went when we were lads.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where would you play when you played out with your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Oh well, I used to - go all over shop we used to go - on Damans Road in - on - in cricket field and - up on Hainworth Moor and - all over - the place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Hainworth Moor is that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Hainworth Moor, yes. Used to go up to Old Gaumless. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 The old what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Gaumless.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It's a pub. And they used to - used to have one of them old - wash boilers and they used to make broth, summer holidays 
and - they used to give us a penny and we used to go up there and be on moor all day, go get a basin of broth when we felt hungry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was know as the Old Gaumless?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It were known as the Old Gaumless in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was up on the moors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye. It's there now - well - it isn't there now, Old Gaumless is done away with, they built a new one. Hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was the Old Gaumless that you got your brother from?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, used to get a basin of broth for a ha'penny and - two slices of 
have-a-cake. Aye. Have-a-cake. Aye. Like that - soft stuff - used to come in and - used to come round at Friday night with it did Harry Law and - had it on - bread plate and then it stiffened and went hard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And you used to have this with the broth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 With - bro}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 th, aye. You - you never see such - stuff as that nowadays.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you used to play - did you have a back yard at Wesley Place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no, that's it on roadside there. Aye. There was no backyard. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You couldn't play in the road, would you be able to play in the road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well we could in them days because there were horses and carts and there were no cars and buses and that like there is now you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you'd play on the moors as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you allowed to play in other children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 s homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, some of 'em would. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were children allowed into your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Sometimes we - mostly they'd - come and - in our house like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And they'd play in the house part?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember any of the games that you used to play in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh used to play billet and stick and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Is there anything else you can think of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Cricket and football, the usual lad's games like. Knur and spell. Knur. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What sort of a game was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well you have a - used to have a - frame from floor and then a arm out and - bit of string hung down or a bit of leather and used to put a little pot ball in it and then - hit it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were playing out did your parents mind if you got very dirty? Or did they mind you getting dirty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, well we didn't used to get so - odd times we would, same as any children like but - there - there were never a lot of bother about that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you free at that time to play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your parents discourage you from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you belong to any youth organisations, you've already said you were a member of the scouts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have any hobbies while you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I used to do a bit of woodworking. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What would you make, what sort of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well used to make - pipe holders and - bit - different bits of fancy things like that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You'd do it at home would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 We used to do some at school and some at home like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have any pets? You said you had rabbits later?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, we always had dogs at home, we always had one or two dogs at home like. Besides what we had for - breeding like down at stable.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember if you collected anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - cigarette cards and - them football playing cards. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you do any gardening at that time, you said your father had an allotment?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I didn't 'til I were about fifteen, then when they took an allotment during first world war like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So when you were at school you didn't do any gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You didn't have a garden at all did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you do any fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You say you used to go and catch tiddlers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I - tiddlers in beck likely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 In a jar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I never - yes, aye, I never did no - actual fishing, rod fishing or owt of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You've already told me you went walks on the moors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you do a lot of walking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, I used to enjoy it. Always have done up to - well I still have - I can't do it now like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have a bicycle, did you ever go cycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I used to have.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. No, it'd be after I left school because - I know I had to save up. A year or two to - to buy a second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 hand bike, never mind a new one. And today they have motor cars at eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So when you went fishing and for long walks who would you go with, did you have any special friends?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, just - there were about eight of us used to - pal up like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 A gang of boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were all of similar age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your brother go with you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not with me, no, he used to go with another - that's because he was a bit older tha-n us like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You told me you played cricket and football in the road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, and on Damens Road or - on mill yard we used to play a lot. And that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were there any other sports you took part in? Did you swim at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I used to swim.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where did you go swimming?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Baths at Keighley. Of course in summer time we used to swim in mill dam and - up at Sugden End reservoir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Which mill dam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Cloughs mill dam on here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Didn't they mind at the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were still young and at school were you ever taken to the theatre at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Any concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 We used to go to - cinematographs when they first started. Ah.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would it be quite regularly you'd be taken to a cinema?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No well they'd happen come at Saturday morning or Saturday afternoon, run 'em in Mechanics you know. There were no picture house in them days. At all. It were a moving - camera like, silent projector you know and - be a - pianist playing
 with it and - captions coming on, and that sort of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But they didn't have a cinema as such at that time it was all given in the Mechanics Institute?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 In Mechanics Institute.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever go to see a concert?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Aye, used to go roller ska
ting a lot, I had unc - I had a uncle that played - hockey with - roller skating team and I used to go to rink a lot with him. When I were quite young, I used to do a lot of roller skating.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Which uncle was it, was it one from Haworth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, that lived in - just a bit below us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was this in Keighley, there was a roller skating rink in Keighley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You had your own skates did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I - yes. He bought me a pair of skates.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That would be quite unusual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He just took you by yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever go to any concerts, perhaps given by the church or some local organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, aye, we went like both to - Ingrow St Johns and Wesley Place and all when they had these -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was Wesley Place a Methodist?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Methodist - ST Hermiter were a Methodist like, but we used to go to all three of them when there were concerts on when we were kiddies like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You never actually performed in a concert?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Or your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there a music hall in Keighley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever go to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, occasionally. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would that be for a special occasion or would it just be when there was something on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well it'd just be when - same as - aunt
s or uncles were going and they'd - say do you want to go with us like, they'd go occasionally to old Hippodrome in them day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your parents give you pocket money when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, I can't say that - I can ever remember 'em giving
 us pocket money. But - when we were at school but I always used to - go running errands for me grandma and - and then - me grandfather were - head man with - heavy horses down here, and he used to always give me tuppence or three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 pence a week and - that sort of thing like but I can never remember us parents - giving us spending money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So your father's father was also involved with horses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, he were with - he were in - heavy horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was he sort of livery man, stable man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, h
e - used to go out with one occasionally but he were mostly - planning the jobs out for next day or - they used to have about - six wagons going to Bradford you know and then there'd be one going - different way and he were planning all the - jobs out and
 what they could get on and all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was this how your father got his job?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I should imagine so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They'd give you a bit of pocket money for doing errands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you get it fairly regularly, this pocket money that you got or would it be just occasionally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I used to get it fairly regularly. Off me grandma. Three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979  }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 pence or something like that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What did you spend your three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 pence on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - now then - well - sweets I expect or s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 mmat like that. Aye, were owt special really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Can you remember at any time anyone outside the home helping your mother look after the house or family, either your relatives or friends or neighbours, do you remember anyone ever coming in to give her a hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. Me aunt - me Aunt Emily used to - make us gloves and sew for us occasionally. Mm. Me mother's sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But there was no one else ever did anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Then me Uncle - her husband, me Uncle Edgar had the hairdressers shop down here and 
- he used to - I used to - lather for him and - that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You used to help him at the hairdressers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I used to - lather for him. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was this when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would he give you a few pennies for doing this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That was a bit more spending money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No other friends or relatives or neighbours would help your mother in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember your mother ever being ill, or confined to bed for any reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't remember her having - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not while you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can't remember me father neither ever being in bed poorly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I don't suppose you'll remember your younger brother being born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 This aunt and uncle who had a barbers shop, they lived quite nearby did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Up Springbank. Not four - five minutes walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were there any other relatives who lived nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Me grandma - lived in - third street from here. Ash Grove.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How much did you see of them, did you see a lot of these relatives or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I did, both me Aunt Emily and me - me grandma like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 With doing }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 errands and helping in the barbers shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother see a lot of them as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not a real - I don't say as she would see a real lot of 'em like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
When your mother did see her relatives, they weren't her relatives, they were your father's relatives weren't they? When they did see them would they visit them at their houses or did your grandma and auntie come to your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, me mother went - called there mostly like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your parents have friends? Outside the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I don't know they had - not any particular friends but they just had general friends like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Friends they knew from work would it be, that your father knew at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, they'd be - friends that lived round in vicinity like, there wouldn't be no - there's no particular friend that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where would your father see his friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well mostly at club or - pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother have any friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not - not particular friends, she were friendly with - everybody sort of thing but not - no particular friend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 She didn't have a friend who she'd go out with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Or who would come to see her a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where would she these neighbours who were friends of hers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, she'd - see 'em when she were hanging clothes out and - call with them or they'd come in our house or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So they would come into the house occasionally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Your mother and father together didn't have any sort of friends who were sort of friends of both of them, such as a couple who would come to see them, or they would go to visit at their home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not very rare - very rarely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You can't remember this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember any friends being actually invited into your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, aye, same as - there used to be some people - a couple from Cullingworth used to come - and they'd a couple of kid
dies and - occasionally and -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They were friends of your parents were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, they were friends both of me father and mother like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How often would they come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Once or twice a year, something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Like weren't a weekly do or a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They'd bring their children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would they have tea with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, they'd stop - probably stop and have tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would this happen on any particular days or occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, just - no, just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When they decided to come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Aye. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Would you say that most of the people who came to your house were friends of your mother, or friends of your father or would they be friends of both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, friends of both really. More me father's than me mother's I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They would be friends from the club would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did friends of theirs call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would that be fairly frequent? Were people often popping in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes - neighbours'd often pop in or any friends that we knew would - often pop in like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would they have a cup of tea or just sit for a chat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Just sit for a chat probably and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your parents ever go out to visit friends? This couple from Cullingworth, were they ever invited to their house at Cullingworth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Occasionally but not - not a lot. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you go with them when they went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I believe I did once or twice but - very rare like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was more them coming to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements, what do you think your parents did when they got together with their friends? Would they play any games or would they just chat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, just - chat that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Many people 
divide society into different social classes or groups, in that time before 1918 did you think of some people belonging to one and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - I don't know. I don't know really how to answer that one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Could you see differences?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Could I what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Could you see the differences in way of life and certain people that you knew? Could you recognise the differences at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I couldn't only - only to say they were -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Perhaps in the way of life of the Cloughs and your way of life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Yes, aye, well there were some people that were - right church goers and all that and - different ideas of family life to what we had I daresay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What sort of class would you say your family belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, just ordinary working class - folk.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
What sort of people belonged to the working class? Could you give me any examples? What sort of jobs did the parents do of other families that were in this class with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - the same as - one fellow - were - well they all
 worked at mill in them days you know. 'Cos they had to work at mill to have one of these house in them days, they aren't same as - they are now, they let anybody have 'em like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So they were nearly all woollen mill operatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, they were nearly all worked at mill that lived in here like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What sort of people belonged to the other classes? Can you think of people who you would definitely say no they weren't working class?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Perhaps Cloughs, you wouldn}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 \rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid879019\charrsid10564979  say they were working class would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh well, no they were - they weren't working class like, they were -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What would you call them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - gen - gentry in them days like. Yes, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you think of anyone else who you knew around here who you wouldn't group with you as being working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Oh well there were - Smiths that lived at this big house here, Woodworth like, they belonged Hattersleys firm. Well I mean to say we used to - they used to always speak to us and speak to me mother but - I mean to 
say you couldn't call 'em - friends at all, they were just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You just knew them because you lived near them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But they weren't working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were they sort of part directors of Hattersley}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 s?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, well they were managing director were old Ralph Smith.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And they lived at Woodworth?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 mm. Just this large house up there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You've already told me about two classes of people, the working class and the class of people who employed people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Then there were - one or two of managers lived at that front street with gardens still like, they of course thought they were a bit above - working class like but
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They were mill managers were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mill - aye, they were - managers down at mill,
 two or three of 'em you know. They sort of felt they were - a little bit better than the ordinary working folk, but I don't know as they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would they be better off than you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, they'd be better off financially. But not - not a right
 lot because I mean to say same as - managers now take about five bob more than }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979  over}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16586785\charrsid10564979 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 lookers in them days and such as that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And their position at the mill gave them the bigger money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They'd a bit - bigger authority at mill like and made 'em - think they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But it also gave them a bigger house did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well, they weren't ex - they weren't bigger but they'd a bit of garden in front, that's all there was, just that end block there with - little - little bit of a garden in fro
nt of each house. Well of course - managers nearly all lived in there, when we were kids.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember being brought up by your parents to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you ever told to touch your cap or show respect in some way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, I were - I were taught how to - taught - taught to learn - respect everybody sort of thing like but - but I can never - never remember touching me cap and - such as that. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there anyone that you called sir or master or a lady that you called madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Oh well - when they went - same as when I went down to mill and - any - Sir John or - sir - Mr Henry or Mr Percy were about you had to call them sir.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 The Clough family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Clough family
, or if you saw any of ladies - now - you had to call them - well I didn't call 'em madam, used to call 'em Miss. Miss Susan or Miss Alice or whatever whichever one it were like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 In the district who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, the Cloughs'd be - in this district and - and then Haggas's'd be more over other side like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So the employers would be considered the important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You did come into contact with them didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I - came into contact with - family more than - ordinary work people owing to me father like and me mother doing laundry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But most of the work people that they employed, did they come into contact with them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Very rare. Well, they'd walk through mill and - but nobody dare speak to 'em or won\rquote t of that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you were rather unusual in that you did come into contact with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Why would you say that they were considered important, these people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well that were thing in them days lik
e if you - if you worked for anybody and lived in their houses you had to do as they - said sort of thing and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think you could say who were friends with the shopkeepers? Would they be friends with their neighbours, the people who lived all aro
und them or would they have sort of other shopkeepers as friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I should think it'd be other shopkeepers, I don't remember - particularly anybody that were friendly with shopkeepers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They'd have their own shopkeeper friends?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about the clergy, who did they associate with, who were their friends? Who would they go and visit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Who's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 The clergy. The vicar.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh well - well I couldn't say that. I can - remember 'em coming to our house occasionally when I were a kiddy but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But you don't know who their close friends were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about the teachers at the school, who would they be friendly with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I don't think they're - really friendly with anybody that lived round here like, 'cos the
y were - nearly all lived same as Otley or - different places like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So out of school you wouldn't come into contact with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. On - only Mr Oddie, I used to go and do a bit of shopping for Mr Oddie, one of teachers that lived at Springbank.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Who were her friends do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were there any farmers around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Farmers? Yes, there were farmers up Damens and farmers up Hainworth and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Who would associate with the farmers, could you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well they used to bring milk round at cans in them days like, well they used to - different people that - they come to here like and - they were sort of friends with everybody like to get - custom and that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 About the employers such as t
he Cloughs and the Haggas's, who would you say they were friends with? Would they have any friends in the working class say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, they used to visit amongst their own - classes like at the big houses.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They would visit other employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Could you say what sort of people went to the church and what sort of people went to the chapel? Would it be possible to classify them?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well \endash  they were - Cloughs used to go to Wesley Place and Haggas's used to go to - St Johns like. And the
n of course ordinary working people went like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Went to both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you would say there was a cross section of society went to both church and chapel
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Going to chapels, oh yes, there were in them days. More than - more so than there is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Where you lived at Wesley Place would you say that most of the working class people had a very similar standard of living to each other? Did they all live in a very similar sort of fashion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, well I should say so. Some - of course the
re were some families rougher than others and - that's because the - parents didn't care as much and that sort of thing which you get in every -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you think of what makes you think of them as being rough, what stands out in your mind to sort of thin
k of them as being the rough families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well it were - the way of life really and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would they be doing a similar sort of job to your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, they'd all - they'd be all work at mill you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So it wouldn't be a difference in income?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, well - there's - same as - they'd all be practically on same income like in here bar few in - front Street that were - managers like.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I'm not quite sure how to classify the managers, I suppose they were working class really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, yes, you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And they worked long hours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh we working - I worked fifty-five and a half hours at mill then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And not getting much more than the other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you say that they had a better standard of living than the rest of the people at the mill, the managers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Managers. Well some of 'em would and some of 'em - I don't think they'd have - they weren't - in them days they didn't get much more than - same as \endash  over-lookers and that sort of thing, well - they w
ouldn't be a right lot better off, they thought theirsen a bit better off I daresay but - that's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Can you think of a family who, although they lived round here and were working class, were sort of rather better off, had a better standard of living, or would you say that they were pretty much all the same, but just one or two rough families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Pretty much at - same like with one or two rough families which you always got.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You can't think of any family having a better standard of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about Alec?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Alec what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Alec Smith?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well they were never brought same as us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They didn't have a better house or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, just had one of these houses same as we had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It wasn't that he was an only child or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, there were two or three - four of 'em. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Did you think any families who had perhaps only one child or two children, do you think they did have a better sort of life than the larger families?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well I can't honestly think of one, not when I were younger like. I always thought we - lived and dressed as well as - any on 'em in - neighbourhood like, that's -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But as you said there were one or two who were rather rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was it anything to do with drinking, they didn't drink excessively?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well a lot - some of 'em - are to do with drinking like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were any of these rough families, were any of the fathers out of work a lot, or just didn't go to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - the
re were a lot of 'em - came from - farmers used to come from colliery district in these houses at one time, and they were - chaps that were - were with that silicosis and that sort of thing and - they used to - one or two families used to - father used to
 be drinking and not working and - they'd a poor life through that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where did they come from, which district would it be from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well they came from - Castleford and - Norwich and - different - areas where mining were, Kent. Aye, Barnsley way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And they were all ex-mining families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
They were all - ex-miners, some of 'em did work at mill but - some of 'em didn't work much after they came here and got their family working, they let the - family keep 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And while the children were small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They just had to paddle on as best they could like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Describe a family within each group, do you think you could describe one of these families that you say were rough? Could you pint out the differences between their way of life and yours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well, same time as - well - well that - may have - a family lived in those street. They'd - three or four workers when they came here and - they used to go down into town and - just fill the fuel bags with coal at station for some coal me
rchant and adle a couple of bob to get beer and then - rest of day they'd spend in pub and come home drunk and - kick mother out and - throw family out if he were that side out and - all that sort of thing. And another couple that come from a mining distr
ict they'd a family - they'd about three workers when they came and three or four at work working but - well they used to - have steak and God knows what for their lunch and kids used to have owt they could - cop on, that sort of thing.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Those that weren't working didn't get much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I wonder why these families moved from the mining areas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, owing to children getting jobs in factories you see, that's why they came this way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They didn't want their children to go in the mines as they had been, was that it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well was part girls and boys you see, that - either go in service or go in mines and - well if they got in here well in textile at that time they could get all family working in one place and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think that within the working class that one group felt itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well you always get odd family that - that does that sort of thing like. But I mean to say there were no reason for it here only just their - opinion sort of thing like. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you think of a family who were like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, there were an odd family that did think theirselves a bit better than - others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How would you say they expressed this? Did they have a better house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, just lived in same street same as - the other families, but they just thought they were a bit superior you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You can't think of any reason why they should have thought this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, it were just their - their thoughts, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Between what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Craftsmen, skilled men and labourers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't think there were any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Around here everyone did a similar sort of job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Same job, yes, aye. There were one or two that were over-lookers and rest'd be warehousemen and such as that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. As far as I know they'd just the same attitude to all - people like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I don't think she were - only she'd been brought up in private a service in - were a bit superior that way like that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think she felt herself to be similar to the people who lived around her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, she never felt - never like felt no better than anybody that - than any of the neighbours or owt of that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was it possible at that time to move from one class to another? If so can you remember anyone who did this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't know. I can't remember it when I were - people when I were younger like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember anyone being described when you were little as a real gentleman or a real lady, and why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well, because it - in them days like you - the same as all Cloughs and all Smiths every - they thought they - you thought they were ladies and gentlemen like. But I mean to say it isn't money always makes ladies and gentlemen is it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you think at that time? Did you think of them as being ladies and gentlemen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well of course I - like I - we both - me father being in private service, me mother being in private service, I were - we were brought up to think that they were all - ladies and gentlemen you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So your mother and father did in fact sort of bring you up to think of them as ladies and gentlemen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You continued to feel like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, well 'til I got older and then I found out that they weren't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That they were just the same as you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think it was that they had money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, it were just simply because they were - owners of mills and owners at factories. And that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 YES. I can.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - I think if there were more like 'em today there'd be a different going on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What were they like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well if he copped you
 doing owt wrong he'd give you a good hiding and - and that were it, if you were doing owt wrong you - you knew you were doing it wrong if you got a hiding and you - you just put up with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He wouldnt' tell your parents, he'd see to it himself would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
That's right. If it were owt serious he'd go to parents like and - many a time without prosecuting like but - I mean to say they were better policeman than what there is today. In the olden days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your mother when you were small ever say I'll call a policeman if you were being naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I never heard - never heard her say that in me life. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Your home was rented wasn't it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Your landlord was Clough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you wouldn't see anything of him as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No, if you had owt wanted doing on - house, doing at house you had to go down, put a note in and then - an engineer'd see to it.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You took it to the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm. Well your - rent was taken out of your - your wage in them days, 'cos rent were not about - three and tuppence or something like that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He was landlord of all the properties around here, what did you think about him as a landlord? Did he take care of his properties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes - they were not bad just as regards doing owt for you, owt of that sort.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were the prices of the houses reasonable compared to houses in other parts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Compared to others they were cheaper than others. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember feeling that your parents had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you feel it then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - well you could tell - they had a struggle to make ends meet when - when we were all younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What did you think about it at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - too young to think owt about - it at that time like, I knew it were a struggle for 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You don't remember your father ever being ill do you or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When there was someone in the district, in Wesley Place, that the people disapproved of very strongly was there any special
 way in which they showed it? You said there were one or two rough families, was there ever a family that was so rough that the people wouldn't tolerate them and that they wanted them to leave?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, there were lots of - people that used to wish the
y'd leave and that sort of thing but I don't think they interfered with them in any - ay or - bothered with 'em like, they just left them alone, that were best thing to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were they in fact not spoken to, these families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - father would be mo
re - it'd be father in most cases but I mean to say - women, they didn't - penalize women for what their husbands were like in any way, they'd - all talk to her and - all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 One or two of the fathers of these families that you thought were a bit rough probably weren't spoken to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, they'd ignore 'em like and - but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But there was nothing else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But I don't think they took it out of - family or the mothers it were just father that they ignored like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You don't remember any family actively being encouraged to leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were never given lessons at home were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 We went at three in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You went full time did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You started at nine o'clock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, nine o'clock and then - twelve 'til - half past one for - lunch and then 'til - half past four. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What kind of a school was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Just an ordinary board school. Wesley Place council. Just ordinary board school mixed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you get to school, it wouldn't be far to go would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, only - two or three minutes just up there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Nobody, we just went on us own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you go with your elder sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Probably I should go with one of the - either elder sisters or the brother, I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You used to go home for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But I mean our mother could stand at door and see us - into school yard like. And then there weren' traffic on road
 that there is today you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You always had your midday meal at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What did you think of school, did you like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I always liked it when I were going like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 W
ell you had some good and - some bad like - just the same as - some teachers that you liked and some that you weren't very - fond on like. I'd no dislike against - any one of 'em really but - you know, you liked some more than others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as important life, such as manners? Were they particular about your manners, how you behaved?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, they would give us instructions in - manners you know if we needed it and that sort of thing. But I don't remember owt - par
ticular - exciting about that
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about tidiness, were they particular about your hands being clean and shoes being clean and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh, well they were always particular about that. And me - me mother was particular about that, never mind teachers.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about the children whose mothers weren't quite so particular? Would the teacher say anything to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, I fancy they would do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about punctuality? Were they very strict about you being there on time in the morning? And in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh I couldn't tell you, I - that's something that I've been always very keen on is punctuality.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you never got in any trouble for that, being late?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you remember any children being in trouble for that reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't say as I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about ways of speaking, did they correct you about your way of speech?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, it was just - no, they just let us go on in us own. - Yorkshire dialect way and never - you didn't get - taught proper Engli
sh, not at them schools in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I suppose the teachers themselves would probably speak with a Yorkshire accent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - some of 'em would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But they never tried to correct the Yorkshire accent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. They never - never made a big lot about - pronunciation and - that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 If you did something the teachers disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Give you a welt at the side of ear hole. Get cane. Oh - just depended if they were handy, there'd be ear - a slap around the ea
r hole and if they were - if they - owt else - bit out of order take it in front of class and cane you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you ever sent to the headmaster?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't say as I were.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did the girls get the same as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Yes. Far as I know they -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember for what offences you'd be smacked or caned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well for - talking or doing little tricks in school that we shouldn't do. Or - anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your parents show an interest in your school work? Did they ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, I can't recollect 'em - me mother may have done but - I don't think me father would. I don't recollect 'em really - being interested in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You don't remember them visiting the school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well they daren't - they daren't in them days. No, they didn't allow parents to visit school and no parent teacher associations and -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 If they had any grievance about the way the child was treated, you don't remember parents going because of that do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't remember any going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 To have it out with the teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did the other children at Wesley Place school come from a similar type of home as your own or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, and - they were all from similar type homes you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't say as they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you were all treated much the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 All treated much alike like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, can't -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Can you remember perhaps whether there was a group of children who came from a certain area who tended to stick together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I think they were just mixed in and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were there any children at school who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, there were one or two - that were just a - sort of little bit backward like and - they like sort of left them out that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They wouldn't enter into play with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They wouldn't like - make a special effort to try and - bring them forward to other standard, they just sort of ignored 'em and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 The teachers would ignore them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
If they - aye, if they couldn't do it well they were - that were it. There were no special effort made with a - a child - a - a kiddy that were backward in -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 He was left on his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, they were - they weren't just quick enough to grasp it well they were just left. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about in the playground, would these children be ignored by the other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well you know someone'd try and - sot of - pick on 'em sort of thing like, you can always remember bits of things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think they would be left out of play generally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no, they wouldn't be left out, ignored altogether but - people'd like try and be - funny with 'em which they are.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you go to any other school after Wesley Place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, they didn't change schools in them days like they do now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you went straight from Wesley Place to part time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Half time at mill and then - worked a year half time and then full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you were twelve when you started work half time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, twelve when I started half time. Thirteen when I started full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think you would have stayed longer at school if you had had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I daresay I should. As far as I'm concerned but I mean to say - in them days it weren't - your - it were your parents you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But had your parents at that time said that you could stay on longer do you think you would have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I think I would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you attend any part time education afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I went to evening classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were saying you went to evening classes, where would the evening classes be you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Ingrow. Council School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would they be run by the Education Board?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Education, yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What subjects did you take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I took woodwork and - mathematics I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You went two nights a week did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you have any regrets about your education at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - it - well, I - I think all old people have regrets about their education, when they see today\rquote 
s standards of education. Because there weren't standards in them days that there is now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you feel with a better education, do you feel you've missed something in like
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh defi - definitely you have, with missing some education.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think by and large you benefited from attending school altogether?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you think what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, aye, well you're forced - you're forced to benefit from attending school. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 While you were at school did you have a part time job of any kind, or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 There was just the half time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Just the half time work at mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you get the job doffing, you were a doffer weren't you when you were 12?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were a doffer for just a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, it were a recognised thing at, as soon as you come to work you went into mill half time, i
t were - it were your father that put you in mill, it weren't - you'd no choice in it like, it were just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you manage to get the job in the first place? Did you go down to the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, me father had - tell 'em and then I should go straight into mill and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you start within a few days of turning twelve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh started same - you started same day as you were twelve, never mind within a day or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Your father would go down and make these arrangements for you to start work on that day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What did you have to do as a doffer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well just take full bobbins off and put the empty ones on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What hours did you work when you were part time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well you worked six til - half past twelve - at mornings and 
- half past one 'til half past five at afternoons when you were on afternoon. You were alternate, mornings one week and after - afternoons another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What about Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, if - if it were your morning week you'd to work while half past - fro
m six 'til half past twelve at Saturday morning. Don't know what they'd think today of that. Twelve year old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What were you paid at that time, when you were doffing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Three and six a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That was just half time, did you feel that that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh well - I hadn't much - you know, I hadn't much opinion of wage, it were what the paid and that were it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And everybody got the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Everybody got same and you daren'
t ask for no more. Used to come out strike - for a three penny rise occasionally - and as far as it come and brace up and send em in and that were it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever achieve a three penny rise by going on strike?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Not as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So father's weren't in favour of sons going on strike?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well they frightened of losing their jobs, it weren't a matter of weren't in favour of getting three pence rise.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you give any of the money to your mother, this three and sixpence?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 We give it all to me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What would it be spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh oh - food and - clothes and -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did your employer treat you? If you came across him at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did the employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - they never looked at you, you daren't - you daren't look up when they were in never mind nowt else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So although you knew him through your father working there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You never actually came across him as an employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Who would be immediately over you, would it be an over-looker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 An over-looker and then there were manager.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you feel about them, what were they like, did they treat you decently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, they treat you this way. He say - could I have a rise like, I'm d
oing a bit more like, I'm dong an extra job. He'd say, aye, bring me them stand steps. And he'd let you get about there steps up and then he'd knock you off, he says, you've had a rise now. Them were rises we got in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That's the sort of thing they'd do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you say that they'd sort of make fun of the doffers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would they be a bit harsh on you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They were a bit harsh on 'em I'll tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there any other sort of punishment that you young doffers might receive for doing anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well, the over-looker - they used to have a - bit of leather about so wide on a stick - dash all fluff away out of passage and that and - they'd be doing that and if they saw you doing owt - that you weren't sha
rp enough they'd give you - a whang with that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you say you weren't sharp enough would that be you weren't quick enough at taking bobbins?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Aye, if you weren't - just if they thought you weren't just quick enough doing a job, or if they catc
h you - larking a little bit of something of that sort you know they'd just give you a - a crack with dasher. Aye, that's what we used to get for a rise, get up stand steps and then knock you off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you get on with the other people that you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you work mainly with other boys of your own age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well there were both boys, girls, men and women and all the lot like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And you got on with them all right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 There was no horseplay of any kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Pardon? Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 How did you feel about the work, about doffing? Did you like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well I don't know, can't say whether I - you didn't mind it 'cos it were all there was - in them days, you couldn't go apprentice till you were
 - sixteen. So you had to - go from doffing to setting and then from setting to taking off and - then from taking off to apprentice then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So then you'd become an apprentice either in a woollen mill or I suppose some went into engineering shops?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Oh yes. Mm. Yes, some left when they were sixteen and went to engineering or what they wanted like, if you stopped in mill like you - went in for - overlooking or - colour matching or warehouse job or - anything - you could just get.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Whatever was available, it wasn't that you had a choice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
No, you hadn't much choice. Well if - if - if my father hadn't have been coachman probably I wouldn't have got apprenticed over-looker as quick as I did.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You think that that helped you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you went full time did you still carry on doffing for a while?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, for a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you carried on doing exactly the same job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I should - we should be on car - we should be on doffing to - happen fourteen or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you carried on doffing but you'd be working full time then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So what would the hours be then when you started full time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Six o'clock in the morning 'til half past five at night, with a half hour for breakfast and hour for lunch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were doing part time work did the job alter your attitude to school in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. Not that I know of. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were working full time what did your wage go up to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were full time, seven shilling. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You still worked, was it every Saturday morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh you worked - you worked fifty-five and a half hours then every Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever work on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever get holidays with pay then once you started full time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you feel it was a fair wage, the seven shillings that you got?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well if we didn't we couldn't afford to argue. Although I expect we did like but still -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you still had all the money over to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Wh
at other jobs did you do then, you were a doffer and you stayed in the woollen mill, you stayed at Cloughs until you retired at sixty-five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But what did you do from being a doffer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, a doffer and then I - got setting and - then taking off. That's like a bit better job but no more money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 All the same conditions of life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Yes. And - I went apprentice overlooking. Oh I went - mechanical doffing after that like when - 'cos all - elderly men that did mechanical doffing got called up for 14/18 war, and I went on - mechanical doffing then. And that were on piece rate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So that would be when you were fifteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I were earning more when I were fifteen I were earning more wage than - more wage than me father. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That was just through a stroke of your good fortune?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When all - with 'em all going soldering. But mind you it were hard work. It were a man's job I were doing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Under normal circumstances you wouldn't have been doing this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I wouldn't have got that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What happened when you were sixteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I went apprentice then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 An apprentice over-looker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What room would you be overlooking, what process?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I went in spinning first. And then I were in spinning 'til I were - I went into army when I was seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So when did you go into the Army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Just short of eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 That would be in 1918 would it, near the end of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 1917. I went in November 19 - no, I didn't, I went in September 1917.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you would be acting as an over-looker, an apprentice over-looker for that two years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you became an apprentice over-looker did your wage go down? After you being a mechanical doffer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What - after I'd been a d
offer yes, oh it went down definitely when I did that. It went on to about seven shilling like I had - mm, to start with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were with mechanical doffing for about twelve months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Be twelve months on mechanical doffing. And then - I had to come down then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And your parents didn't mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have the choice then, could you have carried on mechanical doffing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes, I could have carried on - mechanical doffing, but I wanted to - go apprentice overlooking so -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you took the cut in wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you went back to seven shillings and the same sort of hours? When you went apprentice overlooking did you enjoy the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, oh yes, I liked - I liked job.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You preferred it to mechanical doffing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Then you went in the Army, when did you come out of the Army, in 1919 was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 1919.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What did you go back to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I went back to finish me apprenticeship.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When did you finish your apprenticeship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh about - instead of being twenty one I were - twen - twenty-two and a half when I finished me apprenticeship.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So they didn't allow you time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh no, you'd to make that - time I were up in services I had to make that up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your wage go up while you were being an apprentice over-looker or did you keep on that seven shillings all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, you - it went up - so much rise each year like. Not bar sixpence or a shilling or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But once you became an over-looker at twenty-two you had a reasonable wage did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Were you over-looker in a spinning room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I - spinning and - warping, winding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You varied from room to room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Varied, different departments.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you vary from day to day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. You'd be - some - months in one place and - few months in another and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you carry on being an over-looker until you retired?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And you were still doing the same thing, a few months in this department?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, well - I did -
 two or three months in - colour matching, well I did about eighteen months in colour matching and dying. And I went - down to Becks Mill and - then I went to Coneylane Mill, moved around all the time. All in Cloughs - yes, mm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Why was this, did they not like their over-lookers to become too familiar with the workers, was that it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, it were just a matter of - what they wanted like and - and that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was because they'd be short in different parts and they'd need you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, that's right. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 When you were an over-looker are you simply overlooking the work of other people, or are you doing the work yourself as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well you - no, you aren't doing no - well you - you are doing work, you're - you've all your ca
lculations to work out and - see that stuffs going the right way you know, accounts and - and then you've to see that they're doing their work right like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you have to account for all the work done in your section?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You're responsible for all - in that room where you're in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You're answerable to a manager?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And the manager is answerable to the employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you have preferred another type of occupation had you had the choice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - looking back I may have done, yes, oh looking back I may have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Do you have any idea what occupation you would have preferred had you had the choice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I haven't really because - I mean to say for schooling for another - for one thing. I me
an to say now I can see if I can - if I'd have gone to school longer and - been able to go to school longer, I could have got a better job or a different job or - sommat of that sort but - as I say you'd no chance in them days, it were just a matter of -

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Just getting what you could?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Your father, grandfather worked for firm and your father had worked for firm and you work for firm and that were it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you served an apprenticeship. Did you belong to any trade union or professional organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Trade union, I joined that trade union when I were eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What was the trade union you joined?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yorkshire managers and over-lookers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 It was an over-lookers organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you continue to be a member of that union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I'm a member yet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Is it still called that or has it been taken in by a larger union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, it's still on its - separate union, Yorkshire Managers and Over-lookers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you take part in any of its activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, I were an official for - twenty-eight year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 In what capacity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh - I've been chairman, I've been - on committee, I've been - sick steward for twenty-one year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Sick steward is the one who gives the money out to people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Anybody that's off sick. And I'm - I'm a trustee yet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Is that a trustee of the funds?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, that's a - a funny question like. You - you had different ideas from them many a time whe
n you couldn't get to do 'em. You'd to do their way. Which were wrong, but still it were their firm and you just had to do as they - said.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You had to abide by their decisions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among wor
kers, some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers, did you feel that or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I never made that so. I always - I always tried to - treat 'em as though they were - equals, although they
 weren't equals in wage and all that, I knew that, but I was always tried to treat 'em as equals - as regards the work and always tried to do right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, can't say as it did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you continue to live at home after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And with your brother and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not in any way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You told me when you were twelve you stopped going to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 To church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You continued not to go to church or Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I've never been - never been a regular attender. I've been once or twice, Bessie
 goes to - Christchurch Congregational but - I've been a few times with her but I don't feel no better for going so I don't see no point in - in going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 But in the period before you joined the Army you didn't start attending again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you take an interest in politics before and after you joined the Army, before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I didn't take any interest before 1919.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have any particular views about politics at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I think it was something that never entered me head at - at that - mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You wouldn't get a vote until after the war finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No. After.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were never a member of a political party were you at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, never been a member of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you ever do any work for any of the parties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I've - not actually. No, not - not before 1919 definitely not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you didn't take any part in any political activity at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you in your own mind support a particular party at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I just - supported Liberal party 'cos - me father were a Liberal and - firm we worked for were Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You didn't question it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I never - I just - went along with it. I mean to say I had neither vote now nowt else so it didn't make much difference like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Going in the Army didn't alter your attitude at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You told me earlier something of how you spent your spare time, going up on the moors and fishing for tiddlers sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh, we used to - aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Once you left school and started work did you spend your spare time any differently? Did you have any different hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, can't say as we did really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You told me that once you left school you started to save up for a cycle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And you eventually got one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you would start cycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well yes, we used to go cycling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you go long distances?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 We used to do, me and Bessie's brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You were good friends were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Just the two of you would go off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well sometimes there'd be three or four, but me and him used to go about different - places like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You'd go off for a full day would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you still go to the mechanics to see films?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well I - up 'til I were going - went i
nto Army and then when I came out of Army I never - I never continued with it. I should have gone - I went to Mechanics for one year. The year I were called up. And - I should have gone two years and then gone to Bradford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 For your classes you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Yes. But I got called up me first year at going at Mechanics and - when I came out of Army I never bothered - going to evening classes, I thought well I - it's a waste of time if they're going to make you into cannon fodder when you're - eighteen year
 old, it's -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you didn't continue with your classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I didn't continue to - to go, which was a big mistake. I know that now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And yet it wouldn't have helped you enormously in your own job would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well it would to a certain ext
ent. Mm. Because - because - I mean to say there's these here chaps - since I've like grown up there's these chaps come from university and - they've come to - shoot them in as - top men down here and - they were useless. They knew - they knew all - calcu
lations and all head work and that sort of thing but they were no good at - at the actual work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you go out in the evenings at all when you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, outmost evenings I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Was there a cinema in Keighley then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 There would be then. Yes, there'd be - there'd be - there were Theatre De Luxe down by - market and Cosy Corner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you go to see films in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, you'd go to pictures.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where else would you go in an evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - theatre once a week nearly always when - mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 What sort of theatre was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well, one week'd it'd be variety and then next week a play and - different types of -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would there be repertory companies that came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, they were all travelling - companies you know - used to come.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you play football or cricket or anything at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I never - no - sports, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you make any new friends once you started work, either boys or girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, still kept to same old - local lads around here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did many of the local lads start work with you at Cloughs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes, aye, quite a lot of 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So there wouldn't be an enormous change in the people that you were with would there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 There was still the friends that you'd been at school with, did you ever bring friends home at that time? To meet your parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Well - oh they'd come for me if they were - we - we were going anywhere or anything like that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And they'd be invited in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have any special friends, I think you said your wife's brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
Well there were about - eight of us used to go - together like and we kept - pretty friends 'til we were - all went soldiering and then we seemed to - split up then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you say that you had one particular friend once you'd left school that you stuck to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't know as there any one particular friend like, we just - went with - any of 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have any girl friends at that time, between leaving school and going in the Army?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 I had one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 So you started going out together before you joined up did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Just before I went in the Army.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 And she was the first and only one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Where would you go to, once you started going out together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Oh we used to go to pictures occasionally. Just a walk round - moors and - that's all there were to do in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Would you visit each other homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, not then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did your parents most of the friends that you went out with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Yes. They knew them all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 They knew who you were going with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did they expect to know where you were when you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I don't think they did any particular - as long as they knew - we were doing right I don't think they were - bothered where we went.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, I can't say that I definitely had like but - Oh I were always in in reasonable time and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14366410 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 You never had any trouble about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216634 EP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 No, you never thought of - stopping out late in them days.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-490\li518\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin518\itap0\pararsid14366410 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid879019\charrsid10564979 
\par }}